topPRs.title: Add FCWEED token on Base
topPRs.author: Cocaineeth
topPRs.body:
## Token Information
- Name: FCWEED
- Symbol: FCWEED
- Chain: Base
- Contract: 0x42ef01219BDb2190F275Cda7956D08822549d224
- Decimals: 18

## Project Description
FCWEED is a Web3 farming game on Base network where players stake Plant and Land NFTs to earn FCWEED rewards. Features include Cartel Wars PvP battles, mystery crates, Item Shop and deflationary tokenomics.
